data.description: Adorable 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home in the southwest.  No carpet at all.  All Laminate wood flooring.  1 car private garage.  Balcony off secondary bedroom.   Modern light fixture in family room.  Laundry in garage. Most homes in this neighborhood doesn't have a  backyard, This home has  a Cute backyard with synthetic grass and courtyard in front.   This house won't last.   Community pool.  Close to freeways.
